text:
My brain decided to relate the April fools posts to the lore thanks to @f8tiny1 
We see San in thanxx era, Seonghwa pre-debut, Yunho in wonderland, Yeosang in Eternal Sunshine, Hongjoong in Pirate King, Wooyoung in say my name and Mingi in the current era.

author: Augustina
text: We see ateez escaping with vehicles in the deja vu mv which could support my argument that they are escaping from the upper authorities (the organisation from pirate reboot) but eventually they DO get trapped and that's why we see Jjoong/Yeo in the crystal boxes and Woo chained.

author: Augustina
